// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0041 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 90bde007-9239-5b8d-a845-22690a795058

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:11* OR ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
